README FILE

t7pro
Benoit Dubois
July 18th, 2019


INTRODUCTION
------------

t7pro is dedicated to handle Labjack T7-Pro device (DAQ board).
Provide a GUI to display acquired signals.


REQUIREMENTS
------------

Preferably a Linux system with a Debian distribution (not tested with others OS
nor others distributions).
The program requires the folowing packages:

 * Python 3 (Normally already installed on a Debian system)
          $ [sudo] apt-get install python3

Packages:
 * PyQt5
 * numpy
 * labjack
 * benutils


INSTALLATION
------------

 * PyPi
         $ python3 -m pip install --user t7pro

 * From source
         $ python3 -m pip install --user t7pro-x.x.tar.gz
